videos.headline: Ole Miss comes out hot with 58-yard pitch and catch
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu hits A.J. Brown in stride who shakes off defenders and runs downfield for a 58-yard gain.

videos.headline: Rebels silence crowd with early rushing TD
videos.description: Following the long pass completion, Jordan Wilkins runs through a big hole and in for a touchdown  to give Ole Miss the early lead.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald gets picked on first Miss State drive
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald tosses a ball downfield that Myles Hartsfield reads perfectly to jump and pull down the interception for the Rebels.

videos.headline: Miss State breaks through for punt block
videos.description: Jeffery Simmons wiggles through the punt unit of Ole Miss and swats down the punt to give the Bulldogs good field position.

videos.headline: Ole Miss takes it right back with INT
videos.description: One play after the blocked punt, Keytaon Thompson air-mails his receiver downfield and C.J. Moore is there for the interception and long return for the Rebels.

videos.headline: Miss State puts the ball on the turf and Ole Miss recovers
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson gets hit hard and loses the football and Breeland Speaks is there for the recovery.

videos.headline: Ole Miss trades turnovers with fumble of their own
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu has the pocket collapse and he loses the grip on the ball and the Bulldogs quickly jump on top of the loose ball.

videos.headline: Coach Mullen on Fitzgerald injury: 'It's always tragic'
videos.description: Miss State head coach Dan Mullen explains that Nick Fitzgerald will work hard to be ready as soon as possible after suffering an injury and that the offense will regroup at halftime.

videos.headline: Bulldogs turn it over for the 4th time
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson puts the ball on the turf for the second time and A.J. Moore is the Rebel to recover the fumble.

videos.headline: Rebels air it out for 77-yard touchdown
videos.description: A.J. Brown reaches out for a great catch and turns on the jets to get into the end zone for the 77-yard pitch-and-catch.

videos.headline: Bulldogs headed to the doghouse after 5th turnover
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson passes to Jordan Thomas who coughs up the football while fighting for extra yards and Ole Miss is there for another recovery.

videos.headline: Ole Miss earning their miles in the air with 2nd passing TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu lobs it up to D.K. Metcalf who climbs the ladder and comes down with the catch and then stiff-arms the defender to get in for the 63-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Miss State INT leads to good field position
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu doesn't account for Mark McLaurin downfield and Mark McLaurin intercepts the pass to give the Bulldogs good field position.

videos.headline: Bulldogs take advantage of INT and score on passing TD
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson connects with Deddrick Thomas for the 15-yard touchdown to get Miss State within 11.

videos.headline: Rebels run Bulldogs into the ground
videos.description: Jordan Wilkins blasts through a hole and cruises in for a 46-yard touchdown, his second rushing touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Hill gives Bulldogs life with rushing TD
videos.description: Kylin Hill bounces to the outside and trots in to the end zone for the 30-yard score and is made a 10-point game with a successful two-point conversion.

videos.headline: Rushing TD gets Bulldogs to within 3
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson pushes his way into the end zone to give hope to Miss State.

videos.headline: Onside kick recovered by Ole Miss to seal the W
videos.description: Ole Miss recovers the onside kick to seal their victory in the Egg Bowl.

videos.headline: Ole Miss takes down Miss State in the Egg Bowl
videos.description: Dave Flemming and Greg McElroy break down why this game was more than just rivalry for both of these teams.

videos.headline: Ole Miss takes home the Golden Egg
videos.description: Emotions ran high before, during and after the Egg Bowl between Ole Miss and Mississippi State, but the Rebels were able to take the cake behind Jordan Ta'amu's two touchdowns in a 31-28 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ole Miss/Mississippi State) 2017/11/24 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: The Egg Bowl gets chippy before the game
videos.description: Ole Miss and Miss State needed to be separated a few times before the start of the Egg Bowl as tensions ran high.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (The Egg Bowl gets chippy before the game) 2017/11/24

videos.headline: Fitzgerald carted off with apparent leg injury
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald suffers a lower leg injury in the first quarter and leaves the game on a cart. As he's leaving the field, Fitzgerald attempts to cheer on his teammates.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fitzgerald carted off with apparent leg injury) 2017/11/23
